description:
Subscribe for more Pitch Meetings: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Kq-yEt1iYsbUzNOoIRK0g

The DCEU is no more, and James Gunn is ringing in a new era of DC movies with his take on Superman, which in true Gunn fashion is full of weird monsters, tons of characters, and so. many. jokes.

Superman definitely raises some questions. Like how is Lex so efficient with his little fighting commands? Why does Superman get beat up so much? Is Superman really not gonna help with that one monster?


To answer all these questions and more, step inside Ryan George’s Pitch Meeting for Superman. It’s super easy, barely an inconvenience.
